# Button — Styles

CSS file: `@acko/css/button.css`

## Architecture

ALL visual styling lives in the CSS file. React components compose CSS class names only via `clsx` — no Tailwind utilities in React.

- **`@apply`**: layout, alignment, spacing, sizing, typography, radius, cursor, select, whitespace, position
- **Raw CSS**: multi-property `transition`, `@keyframes`, `[data-theme]` overrides, `@media (hover:hover)` hover blocks, compound `box-shadow` stacks, `filter: brightness()`

## CSS Classes

### Base

```css
.acko-btn {
  @apply inline-flex items-center justify-center font-medium
         leading-none border-none cursor-pointer select-none
         whitespace-nowrap no-underline relative;
  gap: var(--scale-8);
  font-family: inherit;
  transition: background-color 150ms ease, color 150ms ease,
              border-color 150ms ease, transform 100ms ease,
              box-shadow 150ms ease;
}
```

### Sizes (via `@apply` for height, padding, font, radius)

| Class | Implementation |
|-------|---------------|
| `.acko-btn-xs` | `@apply h-8 px-4 text-xs rounded-full; line-height: 16px;` |
| `.acko-btn-sm` | `@apply h-10 px-4 text-sm rounded-full; line-height: 18px;` |
| `.acko-btn-md` | `@apply h-12 px-4 text-base leading-6 rounded-full;` |
| `.acko-btn-lg` | `@apply h-14 px-6 text-lg rounded-full; line-height: 28px;` |
| `.acko-btn-xl` | `@apply h-16 px-8 text-xl rounded-full; line-height: 32px;` |

### Variants

| Class | Background | Text | Shadow / Border |
|-------|-----------|------|-----------------|
| `.acko-btn-primary` | `--color-primary` | `--color-on-primary` | `--shadow-btn-inner` |
| `.acko-btn-secondary` | `--color-btn-secondary-bg` | `--color-btn-secondary-text` | `inset 0 0 0 1px --color-btn-secondary-border` |
| `.acko-btn-inverted` | `--color-btn-inverted-bg` | `--color-btn-inverted-text` | none |
| `.acko-btn-ghost` | `transparent` | `--color-btn-ghost-color` | none |
| `.acko-btn-link` | `transparent` | `--color-btn-link-color` | none, no horizontal padding |
| `.acko-btn-danger` | `--color-btn-danger-bg` | `--color-btn-danger-text` | none |

### Danger Focus

```css
.acko-btn-danger:focus-visible {
  box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px color-mix(in srgb, var(--color-error) 20%, transparent);
}
```

### Icon Sizing

```css
.acko-btn-icon { @apply inline-flex items-center justify-center shrink-0; }
.acko-btn-xs .acko-btn-icon { width: var(--scale-12); height: var(--scale-12); }
.acko-btn-sm .acko-btn-icon { width: var(--scale-16); height: var(--scale-16); }
.acko-btn-md .acko-btn-icon { width: var(--scale-16); height: var(--scale-16); }
.acko-btn-lg .acko-btn-icon { width: var(--scale-20); height: var(--scale-20); }
.acko-btn-xl .acko-btn-icon { width: var(--scale-24); height: var(--scale-24); }
```

### Icon-Only (square button via `@apply`)

Text children wrapped in `sr-only` span for accessibility.

```css
.acko-btn-icon-only.acko-btn-xs { @apply w-8 p-0; }
.acko-btn-icon-only.acko-btn-sm { @apply w-10 p-0; }
.acko-btn-icon-only.acko-btn-md { @apply w-12 p-0; }
.acko-btn-icon-only.acko-btn-lg { @apply w-14 p-0; }
.acko-btn-icon-only.acko-btn-xl { @apply w-16 p-0; }
```

### Content Structure

- `.acko-btn-content` — wraps all visible content (icons + label)
- `.acko-btn-label` — wraps text children

### Full Width

```css
.acko-btn-full-width { @apply w-full; }
```

### States

#### Loading
Content wrapped in `.acko-btn-content` span; loading hides content via `visibility: hidden`. Uses 3-dot wave animation (`acko-dot-wave`).

```css
.acko-btn-loading { @apply pointer-events-none; }
.acko-btn-loading .acko-btn-content { visibility: hidden; }
```

Dots: 6px circles, staggered delays (0, 0.15s, 0.3s).

#### Disabled
```css
.acko-btn-disabled,
.acko-btn:disabled {
  @apply cursor-not-allowed;
  background-color: var(--color-btn-disabled-bg) !important;
  color: var(--color-btn-disabled-text) !important;
  box-shadow: none !important;
  opacity: 1;
  filter: none;
}
```

Link variant disabled keeps `background-color: transparent`.

### Loading Dots (raw CSS — `acko-dot-wave`)

3-dot wave animation replaces spinner. Dots are 6px circles with staggered delays (0, 0.15s, 0.3s).

Colors per variant:

| Variant | Dots `color` |
|---------|----------------|
| primary | `--color-on-primary` |
| secondary | `--color-btn-secondary-text` |
| inverted | `--color-btn-inverted-text` |
| ghost | `--color-btn-ghost-color` |
| link | `--color-btn-link-color` |
| danger | `--color-btn-danger-text` |

## Hover States (raw CSS — `@media (hover: hover)`)

Wrapped in `@media (hover: hover) and (pointer: fine)`:

| Variant | Hover treatment |
|---------|----------------|
| primary | Dark overlay gradient + compound `box-shadow` (`--shadow-btn-inner` + `--shadow-btn-hover`) |
| secondary | `filter: brightness(0.96)` + retain `box-shadow: inset 0 0 0 1px` (light) / `brightness(1.1)` (dark) |
| inverted | `filter: brightness(0.96)` (light) / `brightness(0.9)` (dark) |
| ghost | `--color-btn-ghost-hover-bg` |
| link | `text-decoration: underline` (no bg change) |
| danger | `filter: brightness(0.96)` (light) / `brightness(1.1)` (dark) |

## Active State (raw CSS)

`:active:not(:disabled)` → `transform: scale(0.97)`.

## Focus State (raw CSS)

`:focus-visible` → `outline: none; box-shadow: var(--shadow-focus-ring)`.
Secondary variant adds compound shadow: inset border + focus ring.

## Dark Theme Overrides (raw CSS)

Scoped under `[data-theme="dark"]`:
- All variants automatically use their dark-theme semantic token values
- secondary: `--color-btn-secondary-bg`, `--color-btn-secondary-border` (inset), `--color-btn-secondary-text`
- inverted: `--color-btn-inverted-bg`, `--color-btn-inverted-text`
- ghost: `--color-btn-ghost-color`, hover `--color-btn-ghost-hover-bg`
- link: `--color-btn-link-color`
- danger: `--color-btn-danger-bg`, `--color-btn-danger-text`
- primary hover: `--color-btn-primary-hover-bg`, no gradient overlay
- disabled: `--color-btn-disabled-bg`, `--color-btn-disabled-text`
- Shadows switch automatically via semantic token remapping in `tokens.css`

## Transitions (raw CSS)

```css
transition: background-color 150ms ease,
            color 150ms ease,
            border-color 150ms ease,
            transform 100ms ease,
            box-shadow 150ms ease;
```

## Keyframes (raw CSS)

```css
@keyframes acko-dot-wave { /* 3-dot wave animation */ }
```
